Package userFacade

Class GUIPrinter

java.lang.Object
userFacade.GUIPrinter
public class GUIPrinter extends Object
GUIPrinter is the class responsible of printing the user interface for the entire software. The GUIPrinter methods get called by the UserFacade class, which implements the logic behind the selection of the menu to print.
